				<name type="primary" sortindex="1" value="Shadows of Brimstone: The Scafford Gang Enemy Supplement #3" />
			
						                           
						               													<description>The Scafford Gang are one of the most dangerous bands of outlaws in the West! Ruthless Mutants led by Colonel Scafford and his trusty Lieutenants, the Scafford Gang robs trains and towns across the countryside, making their hideouts in the caves and abandoned mines up in the hills. Former Confederates in the Civil War, they despise the law and use their hideous mutations to fill their pockets with gold and Dark Stone.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This set adds new large Enemy Record Sheets for two of the dangerous Scafford Lieutenants: 'Stone Face' McCoy and &amp;lsquo;Silver Back&amp;rsquo; Pa Scafford, making them full Enemy mini-bosses. &amp;lsquo;Silver Back&amp;rsquo; Pa Scafford is the patriarch of the family and is a new Scafford Lieutenant that did not appear in the Scafford Gang Deluxe Enemy Pack&amp;mdash;he debuts in this new Supplement and a new Scafford Lieutenants game card is included for him. This supplement also includes the new 'Old Blunderbuss' Artifact card, as well as a set of new Threat cards that combine various Scafford themed Enemies together, and even Epic Threats to face off against a more dangerous version of each of these Lieutenants with their gang.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This game supplement enhances the Shadows of Brimstone: The Scafford Gang Deluxe Enemy Pack and Shadows of Brimstone: Dark Stone Brutes Enemy Pack, as well as the Resin Enemy Figures for 'Stone Face' McCoy and &amp;lsquo;Silver Back&amp;rsquo; Pa Scafford. Those Enemy Packs and resin Miniatures are NOT INCLUDED.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
